        %p.lead A kerning plugin specific with Japanese webfont
        %p
          %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-info{href: "https://github.com/karappo/jquery.kerning.js", role: "button"} Get Source
      .row.marketing
        .col-lg-12
          %h4 Demo
          %br
          %h6
            %a{href: "http://www.flopdesign.com/freefont/utsukushi-mincho-font.html", target: "_blank"} うつくし明朝
            \- plain
          %b.example.utsukushi ポラーノの広場
